      "bullets": [
        "Hugging Face's LeRobot v0.6.0 introduces enhanced simulation, evaluation tools, and training loops for imitation learning models like ACT and Diffusion Policy.",
        "The release streamlines policy evaluation across simulated environments like Koch and ALOHA, enabling faster physical-to-virtual validation of robotic control.",
        "Practitioners can optimize robotic policies using standardized datasets, improving generalization in manipulation tasks with PyTorch-based reinforcement learning pipelines."
